Abyssal green dye is an item that allows one piece of the Raiments of the Eye to be recoloured to a green variant. It is a one time use per item, therefore a total of three are needed to recolour a full set.

The Abyssal green dye can be exchanged for an Abyssal red or Abyssal blue dye by using it on Apprentice Felix.

Any extra abyssal dyes the player has can be exchanged with Apprentice Felix for 50 abyssal pearls.
